Class NaiveTankStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • carefuel.util.NaiveTankStrategy

  • public class NaiveTankStrategy
extends Object
    Function that computes the naive tanking strategy of tanking just what we need to get to the next gas station at every gas station.
